title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: You likely feel more relaxed around familiar people you know and trust. Perhaps strangers stir up too many questions and feelings now. You simply are not in the mood to work hard to cater to a new persons idiosyncrasies and needs. You might feel guilty for your uncharacteristic aloofness, but youre entitled to coast along without too many frills or cares today. Yet, your freedom comes at a price. You may need to be more available and present for dear ones, but the chances are you wont mind. You could even cheerfully volunteer your support. You thrive on being helpful to those who merit your confidence. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
